    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Tesh Empire</h2>
        <p>Tesh Empire is dedicated to providing comprehensive information on cyber security, including awareness, threats, and defense strategies. Our mission is to educate and empower individuals and organizations to protect their digital assets and stay safe online.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Cyber Security Awareness section -->
    <section id="awareness">
        <h2>Cyber Security Awareness</h2>
        <p>Cyber security awareness is crucial in today's digital age. Understanding the risks and how to mitigate them can prevent a lot of potential damage. Here are some key points to consider:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Always use strong, unique passwords for different accounts.</li>
            <li>Be cautious of phishing scams and suspicious emails.</li>
            <li>Keep your software and systems up-to-date with the latest security patches.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Threats section -->
    <section id="threats">
        <h2>Threats</h2>
        <p>There are numerous cyber threats that individuals and organizations face daily. Some of the most common include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Malware: Malicious software designed to harm or exploit any programmable device or network.</li>
            <li>Phishing: Fraudulent attempts to obtain sensitive information by disguising as a trustworthy entity.</li>
            <li>Ransomware: A type of malware that encrypts the victim's files, demanding payment to restore access.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Defense Strategies section -->
    <section id="defense">
        <h2>Defense Strategies</h2>
        <p>Implementing robust defense strategies can significantly reduce the risk of cyber attacks. Some effective strategies include:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Using firewalls to block unauthorized access to your network.</li>
            <li>Employing antivirus and anti-malware software to detect and remove threats.</li>
            <li>Conducting regular security audits and vulnerability assessments.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

